
- four tables - users, drivers, bookings, routes
- users - user_id, name, email, phone, password
- drivers - driver_id, name, vehicle_no, availability
- bookings - booking_id, source, destination, fare, ....  urser_id and driver_id, route_id are foreign keys
- user books - driver unavailable - record in bookings
- flow   -     user -> book cab -> driver assigned -> booking stored
- user -> register, login, book, cancel 
- drivers -> accept or reject ride



